  "body": "# Rationale\r\n\r\nRequesting to show `tx/second` in addition to `blk/second` when at step [7/17]\r\n\r\nThis is useful because `tx/second` should be (relatively) constant over time. \r\n\r\nThis ensures that users that monitor progress can see rather consistent progress even when there's a lot of tx/blocks to chew through. This will likely result in less people getting worried about progress. (\"will this ever finish?\"). \r\n\r\n# Implementation\r\n\r\nstats should be readily available so trivial to implement",
